<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="priceless-adj">priceless <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'praɪsləs/    美 /'praɪsləs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>无价的；贵重的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Good health is priceless. 
健康无价。</p></div>

<h3 id="worthless-invaluable-valueless-priceless">辨析 worthless, invaluable, valueless, priceless</h3>
<p><strong>invaluable 与 priceless ** 同义，意为“宝贵的”、“无价的”、“贵重的”。
</strong>worthless 与 valueless ** 同义，意为“无价值 的”、“无用的”。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The house was full of worthless junk. 
这栋房子里堆满了没用的东西。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His comments were so general as to be nearly valueless. 
他的评论太过空泛，几乎都是废话。</p></div></div>